>> +    $ref: /schemas/types.yaml#definitions/uint32
>> +    description:
>> +       Specifiy the DMA burst size(in dwords), the valid value will be 8, 16, 32.
>> +       Default is 16 for data path dma, 32 is for memcopy DMA.
